Detailed Description

cvmx_pko_reg_flags

Notes: When set, ENA_PKO enables the PKO picker and places the PKO in normal operation. When set, ENA_DWB enables the use of DontWriteBacks during the buffer freeing operations. When not set, STORE_BE inverts bits[2:0] of the STORE0 byte write address. When set, RESET causes a 4-cycle reset pulse to the entire box.
